item.description: 250 mg CBD Hemp Oil Heat Salve Liniment For those who prefer mild stimulation and heat we have created the Huny-B CBD salve. Chamomile and Eucalyptus provides a stark contrast with the Essential Oils such as Black Pepper oil, Cinnamon oil, Camphor oil , and Menthol Crystals . Of course there are many more essential oils and ingredients besides these, but the point is that this creates a unique feeling that is just as welcome on sore muscles, aches and pains as it is on healthy skin.
